title: Abortion-rights groups denounce censorship on Meta-owned apps in Latin America and beyond
description: All of a sudden, women contacting one of the biggest sources of information about abortion in Mexico through the encrypted messaging app WhatsApp were met with silence.  The nongovernmental organization’s business account had been blocked.
